title: Fuel briquet

claims.preamble: We claim the ornamental design for a fuel briquet, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a top perspective view of the first embodiment of a fuel briquet, showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a right side elevation view thereof, the left side elevation view being the same;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view thereof, the back elevation view being the same;
FIG. 4 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a top perspective view of the second embodiment of a fuel briquet, showing our new design;
FIG. 6 is a right side elevation view thereof, the left side elevation view being the same;
FIG. 7 is a front elevation view thereof, the back elevation view being the same; and,
FIG. 8 is a top plan view thereof.
The broken line denoting the bottom profile of the fuel briquet is for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
